rComments: Dr.Grison is the sweetest person I've ever met. I took her class last semester when she was carrying her second baby. She must have been so tired but she was absolutely kind and generous. Although you need to study well for her class, she listens to your every single needs.

She is so sweet!very helpful.her classes are really fun because she makes the subject interesting with demonstrations and activities.She is very understanding and helpful and is always out to help you.You havvve to take psychology with her.
